content: <metadata>   <idinfo>     <citation>       <citeinfo>         <origin>City and County of Denver, Technology Services / Enterprise Data Management</origin>         <pubdate>20150226</pubdate>         <title>City Council Districts - 2015</title>         <geoform>vector digital data</geoform>       </citeinfo>     </citation>     <descript>       <abstract>This layer contains Denver's City Council Districts as they were defined during the redistricting process approved on April 30, 2012. These districts were adopted in 2012 via Ordinance 242; Council Bill 286. This layer also contains records for the at-large candidates (to be consistent with previous City Council District layers).</abstract>       <purpose>This layer shows Denver's City Council districts effective for the municipal election on May 7, 2015, and for any general or special council election held thereafter.   </purpose>       <supplinf>Schema modification to add a DOCUMENTS field and GLOBALID completed February 5, 2015.</supplinf>     </descript>     <status>       <update>As needed</update>     </status>     <spdom>       <bounding>         <westbc>-105.109967</westbc>         <eastbc>-104.599538</eastbc>         <northbc>39.914209</northbc>         <southbc>39.614311</southbc>       </bounding>     </spdom>     <keywords>       <theme>         <themekt>None</themekt>         <themekey>redistricting</themekey>       </theme>       <theme>         <themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Categories</themekt>         <themekey>boundaries</themekey>         <themekey>society</themekey>       </theme>       <place>         <placekt>None</placekt>         <placekey>Denver</placekey>         <placekey>Denver County</placekey>         <placekey>Colorado</placekey>         <placekey>USA</placekey>       </place>     </keywords>     <accconst>None</accconst>     <useconst>ACCESS CONSTRAINTS:   None.
